{"tid":2511270,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"原來古天樂同Sony合拍咗部動畫片喺Netflix上","createTime":"2021-04-30T19:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T01:00:04.000Z","uid":15213,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a0289572c5956d691bbcd0713a3943e90b82b8","tid":2511270,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:00:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">古天樂與Sony合作拍動畫片今登陸Netflix <br />\n任執行監製罕有晒家庭照</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210430/24TUQHPJENDQHD5U27ALUJZ3TE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210430%2F24TUQHPJENDQHD5U27ALUJZ3TE%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=0e4a627b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210430%2F24TUQHPJENDQHD5U27ALUJZ3TE%2F&h=8c9e90a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210430/24TUQHPJENDQHD5U27ALUJZ3TE/</a><br />\n<br />\n古天樂旗下的天下一電影公司，近年除了拍戲、做配音、後期製作和簽藝人外，最近更涉足動畫電影。天下一今日在其公司的FB公佈，旗下首部海外投資的動畫電影《一家人大戰機械人》（The Mitchells&rsquo; Vs. The Machines），亦是天下一首次跟美國著名電影公司哥倫比亞影業（Columbia Pictures）及索尼動畫（Sony Pictures Animation）合作，《一》片今日已在Netflix上映。<br />\n<br />\n天下一發言人今日回應：「動畫開發及製作是公司未來發展之一，不斷在此範疇上探求、了解日新月異的製作模式及擴闊視野是我們的首要任務。這次合作正是一個契機，亦為多方向學習及多元發展這理念踏出了重要一步。而投資各地合適及帶有正面訊息的劇本；繼續支持本地新晉導演、演員及製作，做好香港電影及保持探求觀眾所需亦是我們會持之以恆的事。」<br />\n據了解《一》片的幕後班底十分強勁，由奧斯卡最佳動畫《蜘蛛俠：跳入蜘蛛宇宙》創作班底炮製，並由金像監製Phil Lord、Christopher Miller黃金拍擋組合製作，在片尾看到古天樂為《一》片擔任執行監製外，製作人員更特意在片尾晒出劇組各工作人員與家人的家庭照，古天樂罕有地公開其家庭照。<br />\n<br />\n該片故事講述現今科技下，人與人之間的溝通越來越有隔膜，尤其跟家人。戲中其中一幕一家人的食飯戲，爸爸在說話時，仔女全都頭耷耷專注玩電話，反映了現今家庭的實況，而《一》片希望帶出訊息，雖然科技進步，但不能忽視與家人、朋友溝通和接觸。"},{"pid":"3500718fce44ef92badf29bd681b1a19faa4ff10","tid":2511270,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:00:28.000Z","msg":"古仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da80e84ff3291eedf98140dfbef8eebd36eeca7a","tid":2511270,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:01:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/title/81399614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftitle%2F81399614&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=5685b221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.netflix.com/title/81399614</a><br />\n畫風好似唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f601470e9bd4f0f1f1fe96023705efd591d4ccf7","tid":2511270,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推一推"},{"pid":"86afcb0a91512869dc7abc79249a8b4b6cf742da","tid":2511270,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:48:38.000Z","msg":"明日戰紀呢？"},{"pid":"8167f93923f4eab2fdb7e29d9e4b4316cc84b9d8","tid":2511270,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T01:00:04.000Z","msg":"動畫就動畫，咩動畫片"}]}